{"id":9112,"date":"2024-03-03T13:43:58","date_gmt":"2024-03-03T13:43:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=9112"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:22:50","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:22:50","slug":"european-parliament-traineeship","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/","title":{"rendered":"European Parliament Traineeship 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The European Parliament internship programme is offered by the European Parliament in a five-month long programme that takes place in Brussels, Luxembourg, and Strasbourg. To apply, follow the instructions on the page.<strong><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_64 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#European_Parliament_Traineeship_Description\" title=\"European Parliament Traineeship Description\">European Parliament Traineeship Description<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#Financial_Coverage\" title=\"Financial Coverage\">Financial Coverage<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#Traineeship_Period\" title=\"Traineeship Period\">Traineeship Period<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#Required_Qualifications\" title=\"Required Qualifications\">Required Qualifications<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#Required_Documents\" title=\"Required Documents\">Required Documents<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#Who_can_Apply\" title=\"Who can Apply?\">Who can Apply?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#Deadline\" title=\"Deadline\">Deadline<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/european-parliament-traineeship\/#How_to_Apply\" title=\"How to Apply\">How to Apply<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"european-parliament-traineeship-description\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"European_Parliament_Traineeship_Description\"><\/span><strong>European Parliament Traineeship <\/strong>Description<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Offered by:\u00a0<\/strong>European Parliament<\/li>\n<li><strong>Financial Coverage:\u00a0<\/strong>Fully Funded <strong>Traineeship<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Deadline:\u00a031st October 2024<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"financial-coverage\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Financial_Coverage\"><\/span><strong>Financial Coverage<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This is a Paid Internship.<\/li>\n<li>All Participants will Receive a Monthly Stipend.<\/li>\n<li>All Participants will receive a Travel Allowance.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"traineeship-period\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Traineeship_Period\"><\/span><strong>Traineeship Period<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>1st March 2024-31 July 2024 (5 Months)<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"required-qualifications\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Required_Qualifications\"><\/span><strong>Required Qualifications<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>You need a University degree awarded upon completing at least <strong>three years of studies<\/strong>. You must have obtained your diploma at least three months before the first day of your traineeship. You can also apply if you don\u2019t have a degree and can apply with Transcript.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Fields<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>EU internal and external policies, finance, law, multilingualism, administration, infrastructure and logistics, communication, or IT.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Age Limit?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>You must be at least 18 years old to apply. There is no maximum age limit.<\/p>\n<p><strong>I am not a citizen of a European Union Member State. Can I still apply?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Yes. The Competent Authority can offer limited traineeships to applicants from<br \/>\noutside the European Union. If selected, you must apply for any required visas, residence permits, and work permits.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"required-documents\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Required_Documents\"><\/span><strong>Required Documents<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>If you are shortlisted, we will ask you to provide:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>A copy of your university-level diploma.<\/li>\n<li>A copy of a valid passport\/identity card.<\/li>\n<li>A copy of your criminal record issued within the last six months before the starting date of your traineeship.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"who-can-apply\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Who_can_Apply\"><\/span><strong>Who can Apply?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>be aged 18 or over,<\/li>\n<li>hold a university-level diploma<\/li>\n<li>Good knowledge of English<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Deadline\"><\/span><strong>Deadline<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>The last date to apply for the European Parliament Traineeship Program 2024 is\u00a0<strong>31st October 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply\"><\/span><strong>How to Apply<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Application process is online. To apply, please visit our <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/ep-stages.gestmax.eu\/website\/application-informations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">traineeship application page<\/a>:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>select and apply for a maximum of three traineeships;<\/li>\n<li>if you are shortlisted, you will be required to provide certain supporting documents to prove your eligibility;<\/li>\n<li>If you are selected, you will receive an official admission letter via email.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>To apply,<a href=\"https:\/\/www.europarl.europa.eu\/at-your-service\/en\/work-with-us\/traineeships\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"> click here<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"The European Parliament internship programme is offered by the European Parliament in a five-month long programme that takes&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":18380,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9112"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9112"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9112\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/18380"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9112"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=9112"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=9112"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}